# 1.. create a firebase new project in console.firebase.google.com
# 2..  npm install firebase
# 3.. create firebase.init.js and import getAuth to export auth
# 4.. firebase settings-> Authentication > enable  Email and password auth
# 5.. Create login, sign up components, setup route
# 6.. attach from field handler and from submit handler
# 7.. npm install --save react-firbase-hooks
# 8.. 













# hosting steps
# 1) npm install -g firebase-tools
# 2) firebase log in
# 3) firebase init
# 4) firebase deploy
